data.description: Welcome Oakleigh Pointe Community, Where the home of your dreams awaits. This Fully Remodeled-Like-New Residence offers a comfortable & modern lifestyle with 3 bedrooms - split floorplan, As you step inside.. You're welcomed into an open and inviting large family room with a fireplace, perfect for relaxation & large family entertaining. The heart of the home is the beautifully upgraded kitchen, with New Appliances. Whether you're whipping up a gourmet meal or enjoying casual breakfasts, this space provides Eat-in breakfast nook or Dining room... Ideal setting for special occasions and family gatherings. Step outside to the covered patio with an excellent spot for outdoor relaxation, barbecues and enjoying the fresh air. The Garage will allow for 2 large cars, Beautiful Roof 6 yrs young, A/C 4 years young, Hot water heater new 2024, Refrigerator/ Stove new 2024, All sinks and fixtures new 2024, New Paint inside and out 2024
